appName: Wing Suit Flying Base Jump Game
displayName: Wing Suit Flying Base Jump Game
display_name: Wing Suit Flying Base Jump Game
display_long_description:
Get ready for the most exhilarating flight of your life!
Strap on your wingsuit and leap from the world’s highest peaks in this heart-pounding Wing Suit Flying Base Jump Game. Soar through the skies at incredible speeds, navigate through tight canyons, dodge towering cliffs, and perform daring stunts as you experience the thrill of freefall.

Whether you're a casual flyer or a pro stunt pilot, this game offers smooth controls, realistic physics, and breathtaking 3D landscapes that will keep you hooked for hours. Unlock new suits, challenge your reflexes in different weather conditions, and prove you're the ultimate sky glider!

Features:

Realistic wingsuit flying physics

Immersive 3D environments: mountains, cities, forests, and more

Easy-to-learn, hard-to-master flight controls

Multiple wingsuits and characters to unlock

Challenging missions and time-based stunts

Offline play supported

Stunning graphics and dynamic weather effects

Take the leap. Feel the rush. Fly like never before!
